  <brief_title>A Trial to Evaluate the Effect of Rosuvastatin on Inflammation in Patients Undergoing Isolated Cardiac Valve Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blinded, Placebo-Controlled Study Evaluating the Effect of Rosuvastatin on Inflammation in Patients Undergoing Isolated Cardiac Valve Surgery</official_title>
